SOUTH CAROLINA
Pickens County

*Galax aphylla* L.

Rich mafic slope near the headwaters of Eastatoe Creek off Hwy 178. Species include tulip poplar, red maple, black locust, sourwood, few hemlocks, witch hazel, trillium spp., blue cohash, red buckeye and magnolia.

USGS Eastatoe Gap Topo Map
UTM 17 NAD 27 334393E & 3882210N
